sources.title: Western Cyclone
sources.description: Randall (Glenn Strange) is trying to get the Governor (Karl Hackett) impeached so he can take over control of the state. Knowing the Governor and Billy (Buster Crabbe) are good friends, he has Billy framed for murder. Fuzzy (Al St. John) finds the shell and Billy sees it has a peculiar mark. Now they have to find the owner of that gun.
